item.title: Force Remove Docker Images
item.description: [root@selenium02 ~]# docker rmi ad66a5961263 Error response from daemon: conflict: unable to delete ad66a5961263 (must be forced) - image is being used by stopped container 088219585a61 [root@selenium02 ~]# docker rmi -f ad66a5961263
